# рҹҡҖ AWS EC2 Deployment Prompt - El CampeГіn Web

## Project Overview
- **Project**: El CampeГіn Web (Backend E-commerce)
- **Language**: Go 1.21+
- **Framework**: Gin HTTP Framework
- **Database**: MySQL 8.0
- **ORM**: GORM
- **Authentication**: JWT (HS256)
- **External Integration**: MercadoPago API
- **Architecture**: Layered (Handlers вҶ’ Services вҶ’ Repositories)

## Prerequisites
- AWS Account with EC2 access
- AWS CLI v2 installed and configured locally
- Docker and Docker Compose knowledge
- SSH client (built-in on macOS/Linux)
- Basic understanding of DevOps concepts

## AWS EC2 Instance Specifications
- **Instance Type**: t3.small or t3.medium (recommendations below)
- **AMI**: Ubuntu 22.04 LTS (ami-xxxxx varies by region)
- **Storage**: 30GB EBS gp3 volume
- **Security Group**: Custom with HTTP, HTTPS, SSH inbound
- **Network**: Public subnet (for simplicity) or Private with NAT Gateway
- **Region**: us-east-1 (or your preferred region)

## Deployment Architecture
```
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
